longBusinessSummary: KG Mobility Corp. manufactures and sells automobiles and parts in South Korea and internationally. The company offers range of SUVs under the Rexton, Korando, Actyon Sports, XLV, and Tivoli brand name. It also engages in the sales finance activity. In addition, the company exports and sells its SUVs through approximately 1,500 sales outlets in approximately 126 countries. The company was founded in 1954 and is headquartered in Pyeongtaek-si, South Korea. KG Mobility Corp. is a subsidiary of KG Mobility Co., Ltd.
